metadata.name: For A Price
metadata.description:
For a price, He has to lie.
For a price, He has to turn a blind eye.
For a price, He has to be the fall guy.

He is a victim of corruption, his actions are no longer his own
He has no face for it doesn't matter to the ones above
He is kept on a noose at the disposal of his *"Masters"*

Masters that are rotten to the bone
Masters that don't give a fuck about their *"Pets"*
Masters who use them like pawns


[This was my submission for Bill Elis's competition, BillelisRound2]

read full description, [here](https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=15_At1lAC9v_K-RVFR7Dq_Nk2azENdBmv)
